只生成阿史那阙的状态栏
严格按照以下格式:
<div class="leather-border">
  <div class="wolf-head-icon"></div>
  <div class="status-panel">
    <div class="section-title">遇到{{user}}的第{{figure}}天</div>
    <div class="normal-title">{{data}} - {{season}} - {{time}} - {{location}} - {{weather}}</div>
<div class="divider"></div>


    <div class="grid-container">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="icon">💗 好感度:</span>
        <span class="progress-bar" style="width:{{value}}%"></span>
        <span class="value">{{value}}/100</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="icon">🥵 性欲值:</span>
        <span class="progress-bar" style="width:{{value}}%"></span>
        <span class="value">{{value}}/100</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="icon">🍬 依赖值:</span>
        <span class="progress-bar" style="width:{{value}}%"></span>
        <span class="value">{{value}}/100</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="icon">🗝️信任值:</span>
        <span class="progress-bar" style="width:{{value}}%"></span>
        <span class="value">{{value}}/100</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="icon">❤‍🩹 恨意值:</span>
        <span class="progress-bar" style="width:{{value}}%"></span>
        <span class="value">{{value}}/100</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="icon">🖤 黑化值:</span>
        <span class="progress-bar" style="width:{{value}}%"></span>
        <span class="value">{{value}}/100</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="icon">与{{user}}的关系: {{对{{user}}的感觉和关系}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
<div class="grid-container" style="margin-bottom: 0.2rem;">
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="grid-container" style="margin-bottom: 0.2rem;">
      <span class="clothing-item">🥻️当前服装:</span>
      <div class="clothing-section compact">
        <div class="label">上身：{{Upper body condition}}</div>
        <div class="label">下身：{{Condition of lower body clothing}}</div>
        <div class="label">内衣：{{panty status}}</div>
        <div class="label">鞋子：{{Posture state}}</div>
        <div class="label">道具或配饰：{{Accessories and props state}}</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-container">
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <span class="icon">🏹身体状态:</span>
      <div class="body-status">
        <div class="clothing-section">
          <span class="label">身高：{{height of a person}}</span>
          <span class="label">体重：{{body weight}}</span>
          <span class="label">体型：{{body type}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="clothing-section">
          <span class="label">眼睛：{{eye status}}</span>
          <span class="label">嘴唇：{{mouth status}}</span>
          <span class="label">发型：{{hairstyle status}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="clothing-section">
          <span class="label">乳房：{{breast status}}</span>
          <span class="label">腹部：{{Abdominal condition, will change according to pregnancy and uterine semen volume}}</span>
          <span class="label">大腿：{{Thigh status}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="clothing-section">
          <span class="label">阴茎：{{penis status}}</span>
          <span class="label">肛门：{{anus status}}</span>
          <span class="label">阴道：{{vagina status}}</span>
          <span class="label">子宫: {{Uterus status, will reflect whether pregnant and the month of pregnancy}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-container">
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div class="clothing-section">
        <span class="label">🐺 当前姿势: {Posture state}}</span>
        <span class="label">🎇 当前行为: {{描述{{char}}当下的行动和行为}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="scrollable-section">
        <div class="clothing-section">
          <span class="label">🙀 情绪: {{描述{{char}}当下的情绪和心理活动}}</span>
          <span class="label">👃 当前体味:  {{描述{{char}}身体当下的气味}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="clothing-section">
          <span class="label">🧿 特殊状态：</span>
          <div class="status-tag"> {{描述{{char}}的精神或身体的特殊状态，是否服药等等。}}</div>
          <div class="status-tag"> {{描述{{char}}的精神或身体的特殊状态，是否服药等等。}}</div>
          <div class="status-tag"> {{描述{{char}}的精神或身体的特殊状态，是否服药等等。}}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wolf-head-icon"></div>
</div>

<style>
.leather-border {
  border: 3px solid #8b7355; 
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, #2a1e17 0%, #3d2b20 100%);
  padding: 1.5rem;
  position: relative;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: '隶书', cursive; 
}
.wolf-head-icon {
  position: absolute;
  right: -15px;
  top: -30px;
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><path fill="%238b7355" d="M50 15Q...狼头简笔轮廓..."/></svg>');
  filter: drop-shadow(2px 2px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5));
}
.status-panel {
  font-size: 1.1em
  color: #d7ccc8;
  font-family: '楷体';
}
.section-title {
  font-size: 1.5em;
  color: #e6d5a8; 
  text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
  padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: 2px; 
}
.normal-title {
  font-size: 1.2em;
  text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}
.icon {
  font-size: 1.1em;
  text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}
.value {
  font-size: 1.1em;
  color: #d4a657; 
  font-family: '仿宋';
  margin-left: 8px;
}
.progress-bar {
  display: inline-block;
  flex-grow: 1;
  height: 14px;
  margin: 0 6px;
  position: relative;
  top: 1px;
  border-radius: 7px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, #9a7b4f 0%, #d4a657 100%);
  box-shadow: inset 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}
.clothing-item {
  font-size: 1.1em;
  text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}
.material-tag {
  background: #6d4c41;
  padding: 2px 6px;
  border-radius: 3px;
  margin-left: auto;
}
.grid-container {
  display: grid;
  gap: 0.9em;
  padding: 0.5rem 0
}
.body-status {
  max-height: 300px;
  overflow-y: auto;
  padding-right: 10px;
}
.clothing-section {
  background: rgba(60, 45, 30, 0.3); 
  padding: 0.8rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
  border: 1px solid #5d4a36;
}
.clothing-section.compact {
  gap: 0.1rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.clothing-section.compact .label {
  margin: 0.1rem 0;
  line-height: 1.2;
}
.label {
  display: block; 
  font-size: 1.1em;
  text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #000;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.status-tag {
  background: rgba(139, 115, 85, 0.3); 
  border: 1px solid #6b5438;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 4px;
}
.divider {
  height: 12px;
  background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg width="30" height="12" viewBox="0 0 30 12" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M0 6 Q5 0 10 6 T20 6 T30 6" fill="%236b5438"/></svg>'); 
  background-repeat: repeat-x;
}
.scrollable-section {
  max-height: 150px; 
  overflow-y: auto;
  padding-right: 10px; 
}
</style>

所有内容自行填充，随剧情实时更新。当{{value}}变化时，需要在括号内进行显示，例如：💗 好感度: 73/100（+3）；当{{figure}}变化时，需要在括号内进行显示，例如: 遇到{{user}}的第11天
{{}}的内容为可替换内容，输出时没有"{{}}"

